## 5) If you also want DB to have a true LKG tag

Change the DB tag target to:

```yaml
- name: 'AlternaCardManagement DB'
  buildId: '$(DbBuildId)'
  definitionId: '$(DbPipelineDefinitionId)'
  deployedTag: 'DEPLOYED-SIT-DB'
  lkgTag: 'LKG-SIT-DB'
  makeLkgUnique: true
```

But if your DB strategy is only deployment history, keep the deployed-only version.

